==官員及政界回應==

Alexis Jay的報告發表後，從1994年至2012年擔任[[羅瑟勒姆_(英國國會選區)|羅瑟勒姆選區]][[工党_(英国)|工黨]]國會議員的Denis MacShane承認他在此次事件上做得太少，並歸咎於「不想打擾多元文化社區現狀」的風氣<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/11059643/Denis-MacShane-I-was-too-much-of-a-liberal-leftie-and-should-have-done-more-to-investigate-child-abuse.html |title=Denis MacShane: I was too much of a 'liberal leftie' and should have done more to investigate child abuse |publisher=Telegraph |date=2014-08-27 |quote=I think there was a culture of not wanting to rock the multicultural community boat if I may put it like that. |accessdate=2014-09-01 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124185047/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/11059643/Denis-MacShane-I-was-too-much-of-a-liberal-leftie-and-should-have-done-more-to-investigate-child-abuse.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

少數族裔群黨性侵犯多名白人少女的事件也在[[大曼徹斯特郡|大曼徹斯特郡]]的[[羅奇代爾|羅奇代爾]]發生過。[[羅奇代爾_(英國國會選區)|該區]]的工黨國會議員Simon Danczuk認為羅瑟勒姆事件並非單一個別事件，同類罪案正在英國其它地方發生。他認為問題在於兒童服務的管理層不想知道也不關心事情，現在的社工專業充斥着一群只會依照教科書上的東西做事，既缺乏[[情商|情商]]又欠缺能力與遇上麻煩的孩子建立關係的專業人士，即使仍有一些好的人員留下，他們許多時也要被迫採用違反常識的愚蠢做法<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/11066244/Rotherham-is-not-an-isolated-incident.html |title=Rotherham is not an isolated incident |publisher=Telegraph |date=2014-08-31 |accessdate=2014-09-01 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111163757/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/11066244/Rotherham-is-not-an-isolated-incident.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他又認為羅瑟勒姆和英國其它城市的大規模兒童性侵事件被隱暪，與巴基斯坦不良的政治文化被引進到英國不無關係。在一些亞裔社區有脅迫政界人物和團結一致對外的風氣，多年下來已經影響了英格蘭北部一些鎮和市的政治<ref name=telegraph20140831>{{Cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/11066646/Rotherham-politics-imported-from-Pakistan-fuelled-sex-abuse-cover-up-MP.html |script-title=en:Rotherham: politics ‘imported from Pakistan’ fuelled sex abuse cover-up – MP |publisher=Telegraph |date=2014-08-31 |accessdate=2014-09-01 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308141325/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/11066646/Rotherham-politics-imported-from-Pakistan-fuelled-sex-abuse-cover-up-MP.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

自2003年起擔任羅瑟勒姆地方政府領導人，工黨籍的羅傑·斯通在Alexis Jay報告發表當日宣佈辭職並即時生效<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-south-yorkshire-28939089 |title=Rotherham child abuse scandal: 1,400 children exploited, report finds |work=BBC News |date=2014-08-26 |accessdate=2014-09-04 |archive-date=2014-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826223205/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-south-yorkshire-28939089 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[內政大臣|內政大臣]][[文翠珊|文翠珊]]批評羅瑟勒姆地方當局及[[南約克郡|南約克郡]]警方在此次事件上完全失職，並表示必須確保那些犯案者受到法律制裁<ref name=sky1328693>{{Cite news |url=http://news.sky.com/story/1328693/rotherham-abuse-was-dereliction-of-duty |title=Rotherham Abuse Was 'Dereliction Of Duty' |publisher=news.sky.com |date=2014-09-02 |accessdate=2014-09-03 |archive-date=2014-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140904235059/http://news.sky.com/story/1328693/rotherham-abuse-was-dereliction-of-duty |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

前羅瑟勒姆工黨市議員[[肖恩·賴特|肖恩·賴特]]（Shaun Wright）於2005年至2010年在地方政府內閣負責兒童及青年服務，2012年當選[[南約克郡|南約克郡]]警察及犯罪事務專員。Alexis Jay報告公開後，工黨、首相[[戴维·卡梅伦|卡梅倫]]和[[文翠珊|特麗莎·梅]]要求賴特辭去專員職位，賴特初時拒絕辭職並退出工黨<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2014/aug/27/shaun-wright-pcc-rotherham-resigns-labour-party |title=Rotherham abuse report: Shaun Wright quits Labour but not PCC role |publisher=theguardian.com |date=2014-08-28 |accessdate=2014-09-03 |archive-date=2020-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200428114536/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2014/aug/27/shaun-wright-pcc-rotherham-resigns-labour-party |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/rotherham-abuse-scandal-david-cameron-calls-for-underfire-police-commissioner-shaun-wright-to-resign-and-take-responsibility-9697594.html |title=Rotherham abuse scandal: David Cameron calls for under-fire police commissioner Shaun Wright to 'resign and take responsibility' |publisher=The Independent |date=2014-08-28 |accessdate=2014-09-04 |archive-date=2014-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140904232407/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/rotherham-abuse-scandal-david-cameron-calls-for-underfire-police-commissioner-shaun-wright-to-resign-and-take-responsibility-9697594.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終於2014年9月16日宣佈辭職<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/rotherham-child-abuse-scandal-police-commissioner-resigns-but-takes-no-responsibility-9735313.html |title=Rotherham child abuse scandal: Police commissioner Shaun Wright resigns but takes no responsibility |publisher=The Independent |date=2014-09-16 |accessdate=2014-09-16 |archive-date=2014-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140916141704/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/rotherham-child-abuse-scandal-police-commissioner-resigns-but-takes-no-responsibility-9735313.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另有4名於羅瑟勒姆事件發生期間在當地擔任相關重要公職的工黨黨員被暫停黨籍<ref name=sky1328693/>。

2014年9月8日，羅瑟勒姆地方政府首席行政官Martin Kimber宣佈將於12月離職<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/11081266/Rotherham-Council-chief-executive-steps-down-in-wake-of-abuse-scandal.html |title=Rotherham Council chief executive steps down in wake of abuse scandal |publisher=Telegraph |date=2014-09-08 |accessdate=2014-09-09 |archive-date=2014-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140911024257/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/11081266/Rotherham-Council-chief-executive-steps-down-in-wake-of-abuse-scandal.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==各界反應==
地方當局在此次事件中長期把[[政治正確|政治正確]]考量放在保護人民之上的做法，受到英國各界包括[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]群體的猛烈批評。

英國新聞工作者Allison Pearson撰文批評[[多元文化主義|多元文化主義]]對此次長時期、大規模的性侵事件難辭其咎，官員「為了避免打擾多元文化現狀，他們把1400名兒童拿去餵鯊魚」，認為事件或者會成為多元文化主義的最後一顆封棺釘。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/11059138/Rotherham-In-the-face-of-such-evil-who-is-the-racist-now.html |title=Rotherham: In the face of such evil, who is the racist now? |publisher=Telegraph |date=2014-08-27 |quote=To avoid rocking the multicultural boat, they fed 1,400 children to the sharks. |accessdate=2014-08-29 |archive-date=2014-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140829182716/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/11059138/Rotherham-In-the-face-of-such-evil-who-is-the-racist-now.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

Alexis Jay的報告提及與他會面的數名[[市議員|市議員]]相信揭開那些性侵犯事件會為[[種族主義|種族主義]]者提供話柄，吸引極端主義政團插手並威脅社區凝聚力。「英國穆斯林青年」創立者Muhbeen Hussain批評官員以社區凝聚力和政治正確為考量的做法，表示在自己家鄉羅瑟勒姆發生此類性侵事件使他感到很噁心，他認為犯案者大多是巴基斯坦裔的事實不應該成為當局隱暪事件的理由。<ref name=bbc28951612/>

另一位新聞工作者Leo McKinstry認為Alexis Jay的報告提及官員因為擔心可能會損害社區凝聚力而害怕處理穆斯林幫派，正好反映了多元文化主義怪誕邏輯的荒謬。多元文化主義的破壞性影響更見諸於調查報告批評警方即使偶然會軟弱地嘗試跟進問題，也過度倚靠穆斯林長老。「就像英國聖戰活動的受害者那樣，羅瑟勒姆被性侵犯的少女在政治正確的祭壇上被犧牲了」<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.express.co.uk/comment/columnists/leo-mckinstry/504104/Leo-McKinstry-Multiculturalism-to-blame-for-Rotherham-abuse |title=Multiculturalism is to blame for the Rotherham child sex abuse scandal |work=Daily Express |date=2014-08-28 |accessdate=2014-08-29 |archive-date=2014-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140829140801/http://www.express.co.uk/comment/columnists/leo-mckinstry/504104/Leo-McKinstry-Multiculturalism-to-blame-for-Rotherham-abuse |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

美國政治評論員[[里奇·勞瑞|里奇·勞瑞]]認為多元文化主義在羅瑟勒姆不單戰勝了[[女性主義|女性主義]]，也戰勝了法律、基本人類行為標準和文明<ref>{{Cite web |author=Rich Lowry |url=http://nypost.com/2014/09/02/a-multicultural-rape-culture/ |title=A multicultural rape culture |publisher=New York Post |date=2014-09-02 |access-date=2014-09-03 |archive-date=2020-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807132644/https://nypost.com/2014/09/02/a-multicultural-rape-culture/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==後續發展==
2015年，有媒體取得2003年和2006年的兩份調查報告，它們當時已警告巴基斯坦裔朋黨侵犯年輕少女的現象已失控，可是當時警方和社工視那些受害少女是比娼妓好不了多少的問題少女，於是當局便置諸不理。接替肖恩·賴特擔任[[南約克郡|南約克郡]]警察及犯罪事務專員的[[阿倫·畢林斯|阿倫·畢林斯]]表示當時警方未明白[[兒童性誘拐|兒童性誘拐]]已構成性侵犯。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/11583147/Police-treated-Rotherham-sex-abuse-victims-as-prostitutes-crime-commissioner-admits.html |title='Police treated Rotherham sex abuse victims as prostitutes', crime commissioner admits |work=The Telegraph |date=2015-05-05 |accessdate=2015-05-12 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808115804/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/11583147/Police-treated-Rotherham-sex-abuse-victims-as-prostitutes-crime-commissioner-admits.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

據報導，前青年鎮工作者Jayne Senior工作了十多年，揭露了羅瑟勒姆性侵兒童的性虐待行為，但遭到了“反感和輕蔑”。Senior被授予[[大英帝國勳章|大英帝國勳章]]員佐勳章MBE在2016生日榮譽。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.yorkshirepost.co.uk/news/main-topics/politics/charity-worker-who-fought-to-expose-rotherham-child-abuse-to-work-for-victims-1-6895763 |title=Charity worker who fought to expose Rotherham child abuse to work for victims |work=[[The_Yorkshire_Post|The Yorkshire Post]] |date=14 October 2014 |accessdate=20 May 2016 |archive-date=2015-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626164051/http://www.yorkshirepost.co.uk/news/main-topics/politics/charity-worker-who-fought-to-expose-rotherham-child-abuse-to-work-for-victims-1-6895763 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年陸續有一些涉嫌在案發時期對羅瑟勒姆受害少女犯下性罪行的疑犯被捕及遭受起訴<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.thestar.co.uk/news/local/man-charged-in-rotherham-child-sexual-exploitation-investigation-to-be-kept-in-custody-as-new-arrest-made-1-7302353 |title=Man charged in Rotherham child sexual exploitation investigation to be kept in custody - as new arrest made |work=The Star |date=2015-06-10 |access-date=2016-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151218161712/http://www.thestar.co.uk/news/local/man-charged-in-rotherham-child-sexual-exploitation-investigation-to-be-kept-in-custody-as-new-arrest-made-1-7302353 |archive-date=2015-12-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-south-yorkshire-33993460 |title=Men arrested over Rotherham child sex abuse |work=BBC News |date=2015-08-19 |accessdate=2016-01-01 |archive-date=2020-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204204240/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-south-yorkshire-33993460 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年6月據媒體報道當局估計有約300名疑犯涉及羅瑟勒姆性侵案，而該數字將來有可能因為找到更多新線索而變更<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.sky.com/story/1507723/rotherham-sex-abuse-inquiry-has-300-suspects |title=Rotherham Sex Abuse Inquiry Has 300 Suspects |work=Sky News |date=2015-06-24 |accessdate=2016-01-01 |archive-date=2016-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313031419/http://news.sky.com/story/1507723/rotherham-sex-abuse-inquiry-has-300-suspects |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年2月，4男1女因為涉及自1987年起的16年裡在羅瑟勒姆「有系統地性剝削15名女孩」，分別被法庭判處入獄10年至35年不等，另一名被告被判入獄18個月，緩期執行。受害人年齡最小只有11歲，最大是21歲<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.smh.com.au/world/rotherham-abuse-scandal-five-jailed-for-systematic-sexual-exploitation-of-15-girls-20160226-gn53a4.html |title=Rotherham abuse scandal: Five jailed for systematic sexual exploitation of 15 girls |date=2016-02-27 |accessdate=2016-09-22 |archive-date=2018-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180129195052/http://www.smh.com.au/world/rotherham-abuse-scandal-five-jailed-for-systematic-sexual-exploitation-of-15-girls-20160226-gn53a4.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2018年11月，6位嫌犯分別被法庭判處10年到23年不等的刑期。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-south-yorkshire-46222421 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-03-23 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317191722/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-south-yorkshire-46222421 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2019年3月15日，[[基督城清真寺槍擊案|基督城清真寺槍擊案]]的嫌犯携带的一只弹匣写着“为了罗瑟勒姆、亚历山大·比索内特和卢卡·特拉伊尼”(For Rotherham, Alexandre Bissonette (sic), Luca Traini)。亚历山大·比索内特（Alexandre Bissonnette），2017年曾持枪袭击加拿大魁北克市清真寺（Quebec City mosque shooting）。卢卡·特拉伊尼（Luca Traini），2018年在意大利马切拉塔市向非洲裔难民开枪（Attentato di Macerata）。

== 有關報告 ==
該投訴警方獨立[[監察委員會|監察委員會]]（IPCC）開始調查後的傑伊報告警察不當行為的指控。這是IPCC在對1989年謝菲爾德的[[希爾斯堡慘劇|希爾斯堡慘劇]]進行調查之後進行的第二大調查；那場比賽是由南約克郡警察監管的。截至2017年3月，已經完成了9項查詢，沒有關於官員行為的任何答复，但向部隊提出了有關信息記錄的建議。另外53項調查正在進行中。<ref>[https://www.ipcc.gov.uk/news/ipcc-begins-concluding-some-rotherham-csa-investigations "IPCC begins concluding some Rotherham CSA investigations"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ipcc.gov.uk/news/ipcc-begins-concluding-some-rotherham-csa-investigations |date=20170806222923 }}, IPCC, 8 March 2017.{{pb}}
Nazia Parveen (9 March 2017). [https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2017/mar/09/rotherham-sexual-abuse-scandal-no-misconduct-found-so-far-ipcc-says "Rotherham sexual abuse scandal: no misconduct found so far, IPCC says"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2017/mar/09/rotherham-sexual-abuse-scandal-no-misconduct-found-so-far-ipcc-says |date=20170522081941 }}, ''The Guardian''.</ref>

據《泰晤士報》的安德魯·諾福克（Andrew Norfolk）稱，一名羅瑟勒姆（Rotherham）警察與其中一名肇事者保持定期聯繫。在2000年3月的一起事件中，他和一名當地的出租車司機（後來成為羅瑟勒姆議員）據稱已安排Arshid Hussain（可以說是幫派頭目）在加油站將一個女孩交給警察“以換取免疫”。<ref>Andrew Norfolk (16 January 2016). [https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/rotherham-boss-helped-broker-deal-over-girl-zkj9xjzrgpl "Rotherham boss ‘helped broker deal over girl’"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/rotherham-boss-helped-broker-deal-over-girl-zkj9xjzrgpl |date=20210309000036 }}, ''The Times''.{{pb}}
Andrew Norfolk (5 February 2015). [https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/jahangir-akhtar-kingpin-who-had-influence-over-police-0kdgx9d8kxz "Rotherham: politicians and police 'abused girls'"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/jahangir-akhtar-kingpin-who-had-influence-over-police-0kdgx9d8kxz |date=20210308125817 }}, ''The Times''.</ref><ref name=OCarrollHalliday25Feb2016>Lisa O'Carroll and Josh Halliday (25 February 2016). [https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2016/feb/25/how-a-rotherham-gang-with-history-of-criminality-abused-vulnerable-girls "How a Rotherham gang with history of criminality abused vulnerable girls"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2016/feb/25/how-a-rotherham-gang-with-history-of-criminality-abused-vulnerable-girls |date=20170429000003 }}, ''The Guardian''.</ref>另一投訴涉及同一官員，據報導，該官員於某個日期要求其中兩名受害者。一名受害者於2013年8月向警察報告了此事，但​​未採取任何行動。IPCC也正在調查未能根據報告採取行動的官員。<ref name="Kenan Malik (November 11th, 2018).">Kenan Malik (November 11th, 2018). ''[https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2018/nov/11/84-per-cent-of-grooming-gangs-are-asians-we-dont-know-if-that-figure-is-right We’re told 84% of grooming gangs are Asian. But where’s the evidence?]''. The Guardian. ''[https://web.archive.org/web/20201225190032/https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2018/nov/11/84-per-cent-of-grooming-gangs-are-asians-we-dont-know-if-that-figure-is-right Archived Version]''. Retrieved December 25th, 2020.</ref>

一名副駕駛在謝菲爾德被汽車撞倒後於2015年1月死亡，這是一場無關的事故。
=== 2020年 ===

羅瑟勒姆案是引發調查的幾起案件之一，該調查稱，整容團伙的大多數肇事者是英國巴基斯坦人。第一個是Quilliam於2017年12月發布的，該報告的標題為“基於團體的兒童性剝削—剖析梳妝幫派”，該報告稱84％的罪犯是南亞的移民。<ref name="ecwt">{{cite news|last1=Cockbain|first1=Ella|last2=Tufail|first2=Waqas|date=19 December 2020|url=https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2020/dec/19/home-office-report-grooming-gangs-not-muslim|title=A new Home Office report admits grooming gangs are not a ‘Muslim problem'|work=The Guardian|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219232051/https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2020/dec/19/home-office-report-grooming-gangs-not-muslim|access-date=19 December 2020|archive-date=19 December 2020}}</ref>

